lingnewsteam, having reported on professional cycling since 1994.\", \"from\": 10575, \"to\": 10696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before becoming Editor-at-large, he was Head of News atCyclingnews.He has previously worked forShift Active Media, ReutersandCycling Weekly.He is a member of the Board of the Association Internationale des Journalistes du Cyclisme (AIJC).\", \"from\": 10697, \"to\": 10935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cyclingnews is part of Future plc, an international media group and leading digital publisher.Visit our corporate site.\", \"from\": 10937, \"to\": 11056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10937, \"end\": 10948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cyclingnews\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyclingnews.com\"}, {\"begin\": 10960, \"end\": 10970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Future plc\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 Future Publishing Limited Quay House, The Ambury, Bath BA1 1UA.\", \"from\": 11058, \"to\": 11123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11060, \"end\": 11077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8361366188166743e-24, \"text\": \"Future Publishing\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Future_plc\"}, {\"begin\": 11091, \"end\": 11096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"score\": 0.9999999688780012, \"rank\": 3.112187981241096e-08, \"text\": \"House\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_music\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou